OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784724511
OL,3,CHospital letter tech glitch impact
OL,4,C'significant' and avoidable, says
OL,5,Cdoctor
OL,7,FA Jersey doctor says the island needs
OL,8,Fto reconsider administrative processes
OL,9,Fbehind how it discharges patients from
OL,10,Fhospital after around 7,000 letters,
OL,11,Fdetailing information about treatment
OL,12,Fand medication, did not reach GPs as a
OL,13,Fresult of an IT glitch.
OL,15,FThe issue sending the letters from the
OL,16,Fhospital to GPs dates back to February
OL,17,Fbut doctors are now receiving them.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784724511
OL,3,CHospital letter tech glitch impact
OL,4,C'significant' and avoidable, says
OL,5,Cdoctor
OL,7,FIt is not yet known exactly how many
OL,8,Fpatients have been impacted but work
OL,9,Fis now underway to contact those
OL,10,Faffected.
OL,12,FHowever, one GP, Dr Maitiu Tuathail,
OL,13,Ftold ITV News that the problem has
OL,14,Fcaused a practices a major headache.
OL,16,FDr Tuathail said: "It will be a
OL,17,Fsignificant administrative burden for
OL,18,FGPs. There is a significant patient
OL,19,Fsafety issue so we'll work
OL,20,Fcollaboratively with the hospital to
OL,21,Fmake sure things are satisfactory.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784724511
OL,3,CHospital letter tech glitch impact
OL,4,C'significant' and avoidable, says
OL,5,Cdoctor
OL,7,F"In the UK, what's the accepted norm
OL,8,Fis that patients are actually given a
OL,9,Fcopy of their discharge letters when
OL,10,Fthey leave the hospital and we hope
OL,11,Fthat going forward, that's what we'd
OL,12,Faspire to achieve here in Jersey.
OL,14,F"If we were doing that from the start,
OL,15,Fthis would've never happened."
OL,17,FITV News spoke to one affected
OL,18,Fpatient, who says the fault has left
OL,19,Fthem without one form of treatment
OL,20,Fthey need.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784724511
OL,3,CHospital letter tech glitch impact
OL,4,C'significant' and avoidable, says
OL,5,Cdoctor
OL,7,FThey said: "I was expecting an urgent
OL,8,Freferral to another department. I was
OL,9,Falso prescribed some medication that
OL,10,Fmy GP should've been aware of and she
OL,11,Fwas unable to prescribe it for me."
OL,13,FJersey's Health Minister, Senator Tom
OL,14,FBinet, says work to understand the
OL,15,Fscale of the impact is happening at
OL,16,Fpace.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1784724511
OL,3,CHospital letter tech glitch impact
OL,4,C'significant' and avoidable, says
OL,5,Cdoctor
OL,7,FSenator Binet said: "It's difficult to
OL,8,Fknow the extent to which anyone has
OL,9,Fbeen affected at this stage because
OL,10,Fthey've got to go through that process
OL,11,Fwhich they're going to go through as
OL,12,Fquickly as they can.
OL,14,F"I haven't got an end date because
OL,15,Fit's difficult to estimate but I know
OL,16,Fthat everyone is working their best to
OL,17,Fget this done."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
